-- Alitalia to cut less than 5,000 jobs, minister says
-- 
-- Thu Sep 4, 2008 12:47pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/04/us-alitalia-layoffs-idUSRAT00400220080904

 

 ROME  (Reuters) - Layoffs at bankrupt airline Alitalia AZPIa.MI should be less than 5,000, Italy's Labour Minister Maurizio Sacconi said on Thursday after meeting with unions. 

 "I expect there will be less than 5,000 (job cuts)," he said. (Reporting by  Alberto Sisto )